// @mui material components
import Card from "@mui/material/Card";
import Typography from "@mui/material/Typography";
import Link from "@mui/material/Link";
import Box from "@mui/material/Box";

// examples
import DashboardLayout from "examples/LayoutContainers/DashboardLayout";

// base styles
import typography from "assets/theme/base/typography";

// Argon Dashboard 2 MUI context
import { useArgonController } from "context";

function VRInfo() {
  const { fontWeightMedium } = typography;
  const [controller] = useArgonController();
  const { darkMode } = controller;


  // Set text color based on the current mode
  const textColor = darkMode ? "white" : "black";

  return (
    <DashboardLayout>
      <Box sx={{ padding: 3 }}>
        <Card sx={{ marginBottom: 3, padding: 2, backgroundColor: darkMode ? "#fff" : "#fff" }}>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={fontWeightMedium} color={textColor} gutterBottom>
            Literacy and Educational Modules
          </Typography>
          <Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color={textColor}>
               PERSONAL FINANCES 
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
              An overview of making and overseeing personal budgets for goal-setting and financial stability.                <Link href="https://www.investopedia.com/terms/b/budget.asp" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" sx={{ marginLeft: 1, color: darkMode ? "lightblue" : "blue" }}>
                </Link>
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color={textColor}>
                ⁠MUTUAL FUNDS 
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
              Describes the many kinds of mutual funds and how they are used to lower risks and diversify investments.
                <Link href="https://www.amfiindia.com/investor-corner/knowledge-center/introduction-to-mutual-funds.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" sx={{ marginLeft: 1, color: darkMode ? "lightblue" : "blue" }}>
                  Learn More
                </Link>
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color={textColor}>
              STOCK MARKET
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
              A summary of the composition of the Indian stock market, how stocks are exchanged, and crucial advice for investors.
                <Link href="https://www.investopedia.com/articles/stocks/09/indian-stock-market.asp" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" sx={{ marginLeft: 1, color: darkMode ? "lightblue" : "blue" }}>
                  Learn More
                </Link>
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Card>

        {/* Wealth Management Tips */}
        <Card sx={{ marginBottom: 3, padding: 2, backgroundColor: darkMode ? "#fff" : "#fff" }}>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={fontWeightMedium} color={textColor} gutterBottom>
            Wealth Management Tips
          </Typography>
          <Box>
            {/* Example Tips */}
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Tip 1: Diversify your investments to spread risk and achieve better returns over the long term.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Tip 2: Invest regularly, even in small amounts, to benefit from compounding and build wealth steadily.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Tip 3: Reassess your financial goals and risk tolerance regularly to make informed investment decisions.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color={textColor}>
                Further Reading: Managing Wealth During Market Fluctuations
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Get expert advice on staying resilient during market downturns and make well-informed financial decisions.
                <Link href="https://example.com/market-fluctuations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" sx={{ marginLeft: 1, color: darkMode ? "lightblue" : "blue" }}>
                  Learn More
                </Link>
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Card>

        {/* Financial Guidance and Investments */}
        <Card sx={{ padding: 2, backgroundColor: darkMode ? "#fff" : "#fff" }}>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={fontWeightMedium} color={textColor} gutterBottom>
            Financial Guidance and Investments
          </Typography>
          <Box>
            {/* Example Content for Financial Guidance */}
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Set clear financial goals, whether it’s saving for retirement, buying a home, or building an emergency fund.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Diversify your investments across asset classes to minimize risk and potentially increase returns.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Consult a financial advisor to understand which investment options best fit your financial goals and risk profile.
              </Typography>
            </Box>

            {/* Example of Questions for Chatbot */}
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
  <Typography variant="h6" color={textColor}>
    Questions You Can Ask Our Chatbot:
  </Typography>
  <Box>
    <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
      “What is the best way to start investing?”
    </Typography>
    <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
      “How can I diversify my investment portfolio?”
    </Typography>
    <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
      “What are the benefits of long-term investing?”
    </Typography>
    <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
      “How do I prepare for retirement?”
    </Typography>
  </Box>
</Box>

            {/* External Resource for Investment Insights */}
            <Box sx={{ marginBottom: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color={textColor}>
                Investment Insights
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color={textColor}>
                Explore top-performing funds and stocks that align with your financial objectives.
                <Link href="https://example.com/investment-insights" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" sx={{ marginLeft: 1, color: darkMode ? "lightblue" : "blue" }}>
                  Learn More
                </Link>
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Card>
      </Box>
    </DashboardLayout>
  );
}

export default VRInfo;
